raw_data.description: Provide full-time unsupervised on-site support operating and maintaining the Joint Theater Air-to-Ground Simulation Systems (JTAGSS), Airborne Warning and Control Systems (AWACS), Airborne Surveillance Command and Control (ASC2), and/or Theater Air Control System (TACS) training and ground systems and networks; operate and maintain C2ISR system hardware and software; perform limited analysis to determine system viability and accuracy. Instruct, train and oversee assigned Training System Engineer I personnel in all facets of C2ISR System operations as directed. Maintain Department of Defense (DoD) 8570 Information Assurance Technician (IAT) Level 2 certification.
